T*
(- Transaction Hashing Roles) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Atho distinguishes digest roles clearly:) Tj
T*
(- txid: deterministic no-witness identity hash.) Tj
T*
(- wtxid: full transaction hash including witness payload.) Tj
T*
(- signing digest: canonical no-witness signing body hash.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Operational impact:) Tj
T*
(- tx indexing and validation use stable digest semantics,) Tj
T*
(- witness malleability is isolated from no-witness identity where intended,) Tj
T*
(- signing verification always rebuilds canonical signing body before hashing.) Tj
T*
(- Block and Runtime Identity) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Block-level identity paths also rely on SHA3-384 conventions so digest width and tooling are) Tj
T*
(consistent. The same primitive family is reused in binary pinning metadata, creating a cohesive) Tj
T*
(integrity model across consensus and runtime binaries.) Tj
